Hello lovely people, I'm Samra! I'm an urban planner and engineer with experience in project management, risk management, and data analytics. I'm so happy to be a part of this effort!

After we have successfully delivered on the asks from the Ministry of Health, I would love to brainstorm ways we can activate existing networks for mutual aid and resource sharing using tech:
1. develop a process to assess people’s needs 
2. develop a process to assess what you can give and 
3. develop a process of updating those two processes in a transparent public and autotomized way
existing networks can be: mehabers, neighborhood or city organizations, LOCAL religious orgs, informal medical or funerary groups, or leagues of sports teams, etc.)
